001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 65,
009    displayName = "Bolus Requested 2/3",
010    internalName = "LID_BOLUS_REQUESTED_MSG2",
011    usedByAndroid = true,
012    usedByTidepool = true
013)
014public class BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    private int bolusId;
017    private int options;
018    private int standardPercent;
019    private int duration;
020    private int spare1;
021    private int isf;
022    private int targetBG;
023    private boolean userOverride;
024    private boolean declinedCorrection;
025    private int selectedIOB;
026    private int spare2;
027    
028    public BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog() {}
029    
030    public BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int options, int standardPercent, int duration, int spare1, int isf, int targetBG, boolean userOverride, boolean declinedCorrection, int selectedIOB, int spare2) {
031        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, bolusId, options, standardPercent, duration, spare1, isf, targetBG, userOverride, declinedCorrection, selectedIOB, spare2);
032        this.pumpTimeSec = pumpTimeSec;
033        this.sequenceNum = sequenceNum;
034        this.bolusId = bolusId;
035        this.options = options;
036        this.standardPercent = standardPercent;
037        this.duration = duration;
038        this.spare1 = spare1;
039        this.isf = isf;
040        this.targetBG = targetBG;
041        this.userOverride = userOverride;
042        this.declinedCorrection = declinedCorrection;
043        this.selectedIOB = selectedIOB;
044        this.spare2 = spare2;
045    }
046
047    public BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog(int bolusId, int options, int standardPercent, int duration, int spare1, int isf, int targetBG, boolean userOverride, boolean declinedCorrection, int selectedIOB, int spare2) {
048        this(0, 0, bolusId, options, standardPercent, duration, spare1, isf, targetBG, userOverride, declinedCorrection, selectedIOB, spare2);
049    }
050
051    public int typeId() {
052        return 65;
053    }
054
055    /**
056     * <table border="1">
057     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog:</caption>
058     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
059     * <tr><td><code>options</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
060     * <tr><td><code>standardPercent</code></td><td><code>raw[13]</code></td></tr>
061     * <tr><td><code>duration</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
062     * <tr><td><code>spare1</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
063     * <tr><td><code>isf</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
064     * <tr><td><code>targetBG</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 20)</code></td></tr>
065     * <tr><td><code>userOverride</code></td><td><code>raw[22] != 0</code></td></tr>
066     * <tr><td><code>declinedCorrection</code></td><td><code>raw[23] != 0</code></td></tr>
067     * <tr><td><code>selectedIOB</code></td><td><code>raw[24]</code></td></tr>
068     * <tr><td><code>spare2</code></td><td><code>raw[1]</code></td></tr>
069     * </table>
070     */
071    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
072        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
073        this.cargo = raw;
074        parseBase(raw);
075        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
076        this.options = raw[12];
077        this.standardPercent = raw[13];
078        this.duration = Bytes.readShort(raw, 14);
079        this.spare1 = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
080        this.isf = Bytes.readShort(raw, 18);
081        this.targetBG = Bytes.readShort(raw, 20);
082        this.userOverride = raw[22] != 0;
083        this.declinedCorrection = raw[23] != 0;
084        this.selectedIOB = raw[24];
085        this.spare2 = raw[1];
086        
087    }
088
089    
090    /**
091     * <table border="1">
092     * <caption>Byte layout for BolusRequestedMsg2HistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
093     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
094     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{(byte) 65} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
096     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
097     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
098     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
099     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
100     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
101     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
102     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
103     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
104     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
105     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
106     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>(byte) options</code></td></tr>
107     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>(byte) standardPercent</code></td></tr>
108     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(duration) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
109     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(duration) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
110     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare1) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
111     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare1) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
112     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(isf) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
113     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(isf) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
114     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(targetBG) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
115     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(targetBG) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
116     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>(byte) (userOverride ? 1 : 0)</code></td></tr>
117     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>(byte) (declinedCorrection ? 1 : 0)</code></td></tr>
118     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>(byte) selectedIOB</code></td></tr>
119     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>(byte) spare2</code></td></tr>
120     * </table>
121     */
122    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int bolusId, int options, int standardPercent, int duration, int spare1, int isf, int targetBG, boolean userOverride, boolean declinedCorrection, int selectedIOB, int spare2) {
123        return Bytes.combine(
124            new byte[] { (byte) 65, 0},
125            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
126            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
127            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
128            new byte[]{ (byte) options }, 
129            new byte[]{ (byte) standardPercent }, 
130            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(duration), 
131            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(spare1), 
132            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(isf), 
133            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(targetBG), 
134            new byte[]{ (byte) (userOverride ? 1 : 0) }, 
135            new byte[]{ (byte) (declinedCorrection ? 1 : 0) }, 
136            new byte[]{ (byte) selectedIOB }, 
137            new byte[]{ (byte) spare2 });
138    }
139
140    /**
141     * @return bolus ID
142     */
143    public int getBolusId() {
144        return bolusId;
145    }
146    public int getOptions() {
147        return options;
148    }
149
150    /**
151     * @return 100 if a standard bolus, otherwise the percent of the bolus which is performed up
152     * front in an extended bolus
153     */
154    public int getStandardPercent() {
155        return standardPercent;
156    }
157
158    /**
159     * @return 0 if a standard bolus, otherwise the duration between the standard and extended bolus
160     */
161    public int getDuration() {
162        return duration;
163    }
164
165    public int getSpare1() {
166        return spare1;
167    }
168
169    /**
170     * @return insulin sensitivity factor in the insulin delivery profile
171     */
172    public int getIsf() {
173        return isf;
174    }
175
176    /**
177     * @return target BG in mg/dL in the insulin delivery profile
178     */
179    public int getTargetBG() {
180        return targetBG;
181    }
182
183    /**
184     * @return true if the user overrode the insulin delivery amount (i.e., not calculated just
185     * from the combination of carbs + BG correction)
186     */
187    public boolean getUserOverride() {
188        return userOverride;
189    }
190
191    /**
192     * @return true if the correction amount due to the current BG+IOB was declined
193     */
194    public boolean getDeclinedCorrection() {
195        return declinedCorrection;
196    }
197
198    /**
199     * @return TODO(unknown)
200     */
201    public int getSelectedIOB() {
202        return selectedIOB;
203    }
204    public int getSpare2() {
205        return spare2;
206    }
